        <abstract>
            <p>Describes plans to publish English edition of Krause’s work on Erasmus Darwin.</p> 
<p>Will correct Anna Seward’s calumnies [in <hi rend="italic">Memoirs of the life of Dr Darwin</hi> (1804)].</p> 
            <p>Asks about family letters.</p> 
<p>Doubts some stories about Erasmus Darwin [in Christiana C. Hankin, ed., <hi rend="italic">Life of Mary Anne Schimmelpenninck</hi> (1858)].</p> 
        </abstract>
